&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build fault-tolerant, horizontally scalable solutions running in multi-tenant environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
